This implementation is based on the research paper:

"A-Mem: Agentic Memory for LLM Agents"
by Wujiang Xu, Zujie Liang, Kai Mei, Hang Gao, Juntao Tan, Yongfeng Zhang
Rutgers University, Independent Researcher, AIOS Foundation

Paper: https://arxiv.org/html/2502.12110v11

Original Code Repositories:
- Benchmark Evaluation: https://github.com/WujiangXu/AgenticMemory
- Production-ready System: https://github.com/WujiangXu/A-mem-sys

